high_descs: Turn around and walk towards the wall, then turn left and walk up to the sink counter.
Pick up the furthest toilet paper roll off of the counter.
Turn around and walk towards the door, then turn around to face the counter.
Open the rightmost drawer below the counter and put the toilet paper roll in on the right side.
Turn left and walk forward, then turn right and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the toilet paper tube off of the counter.
Turn right and take a step forward, then turn right again and walk towards the door, turn around to face the counter.
Open the rightmost drawer and put the toilet paper tube inside to the left of the toilet paper roll that's already in there.
anns.task_desc: Move two toilet paper tube to a drawer.

high_descs: Move across the room to the center of the vanity in between the sinks.
Pick up the full roll of toilet paper that is closest to the back.
Move to the right side of the vanity.
Open the bottom drawer on the right hand side.  Put the roll of toilet paper inside the drawer. Close the drawer.
Move back to the left to the center of the vanity in between the sinks.
Pick up the empty toilet paper roll off of the counter.
Move to the right side of the vanity.
Open the bottom drawer on the right hand side.  Put the empty toilet paper roll inside the drawer. Close the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Move 2 rolls of toilet paper - one empty, one full - to the lower right drawer of the vanity.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the counter with two sinks on your left.
Pick up the roll of toilet paper that is behind a perfume bottle on this counter.
Back up from the counter a bit and open the drawer underneath the right sink.
Place the roll of toilet paper in this drawer.
Walk back to the middle of the counter.
Pick up the empty roll of toilet paper from between the two candles.
Walk back to where you can access the drawer under the right sink.
Place the empty roll in the drawer.
anns.task_desc: Place two rolls of toilet paper, one empty, one full, in a drawer.
